summary: And at last I see the light And it's like the fog has lifted And at last I see the light And it's like the sky is new And it's...
caption:
And at last I see the light
And it’s like the fog has lifted
And at last I see the light
And it’s like the sky is new
And it’s warm and real and bright
And the world has somehow shifted
All at once everything looks different
Now that I see you

———————-

Been wanting to do this for a while. I love Tangled. It’s my second favourite Disney princess movie and I always thought that Tamara and Ookami fitted Flynn and Rapunzel the best out of all of the Disney couples. One is a sweet girl and the other is a charming guy.


Couldn’t be bother with shading so I left it like this

This picture has oc x canon stuff in it so if that is not your cup of tea then leave.
